channel.title: Pmod Meeting Place Coords
channel.description:
In the 508+ I'm not sure which cache the pmod in game meeting place came in but I was just wondering if anyone has found the coords to the place? I've seen this place for myself but the location isn't known because it's just a random room in the middle of no where, so it would be tricky to find.
Does anyone know?
